            "text_pkrhc9": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Sustainability means thinking long term and acting with care across the full system of what we do.</p><p>As an island-based project, we work in close relationship with limited and precious resources. Water is scarce, ecosystems are delicate and every decision carries weight.</p><p>For us, sustainability means using those resources responsibly, minimising harm and making choices that support the long-term health of the land, the integrity of the products we create.</p><p>It also means recognising that sustainability is not perfection. It is a practice of continuous improvement. Learning, refining, and evolving over time.</p>",
